tle=\"Editar secciÃ³n: Unidad imaginaria\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(84, 89, 93);\">]</span></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Se define un nÃºmero complejo especial, sobre todo en el Ã¡lgebra, de suma relevancia, el nÃºmero<span>&nbsp;</span><i>i</i><span>&nbsp;</span>(<span>&nbsp;</span><i>j</i><span>&nbsp;</span>en fÃ­sica), llamado<b>unidad imaginaria</b>, definido como</p><dl style=\"margin-top: 0.2em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><dd style=\"margin-left: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.1em; margin-right: 0px;\"><span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; opacity: 0;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{displaystyle mathrm {i} =(0,1),!}</annotation></semantics></math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/b40d9ec737e98a798a9ff588a77d908a915a9524\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline\" aria-hidden=\"true\" alt=\"{mathrm  {i}}=(0,1),!\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: -0.838ex; display: inline-block; margin-right: -0.387ex; width: 9.301ex; height: 2.843ex;\"></span></dd></dl><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Que satisface la siguiente igualdad:</p><dl style=\"margin-top: 0.2em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><dd style=\"margin-left: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.1em; margin-right: 0px;\"><span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; opacity: 0;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{displaystyle mathrm {i} ^{2}=mathrm {i} cdot mathrm {i} =(0,1)cdot (0,1)=(-1,0)=-1}</annotation></semantics></math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/cbdbfe7b40ec2a0b1e7185fd0f05c0bbb3fc98ee\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline\" aria-hidden=\"true\" alt=\"{mathrm  {i}}^{2}={mathrm  {i}}cdot {mathrm  {i}}=(0,1)cdot (0,1)=(-1,0)=-1\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: -0.838ex; display: inline-block; width: 39.03ex; height: 3.176ex;\"></span></dd></dl><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Tomando en cuenta que<span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; opacity: 0;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{displaystyle (a,0)cdot (0,1)=(0,a)}</annotation></semantics></math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/f0eac98449fc11c5f92560272011c86a37a0cc34\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline\" aria-hidden=\"true\" alt=\"(a,0)cdot (0,1)=(0,a)\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: -0.838ex; margin: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 20.417ex; height: 2.843ex;\"></span>, cabe la identificaciÃ³n</p><dl style=\"margin-top: 0.2em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decorat