lor: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 302px;\"><a href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Euler%27s_formula.svg\" class=\"image\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/71/Euler%27s_formula.svg/300px-Euler%27s_formula.svg.png\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-file-width=\"512\" data-file-height=\"549\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" width=\"300\" height=\"322\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\">La<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/F%C3%B3rmula_de_Euler\" title=\"FÃ³rmula de Euler\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;\">fÃ³rmula de Euler</a><span>&nbsp;</span>ilustrada en el<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plano_complejo\" title=\"Plano complejo\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;\">plano complejo</a>.</div></div></div><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">El<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Valor_absoluto\" title=\"Valor absoluto\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;\">valor absoluto</a>,<span>&nbsp;</span><i>mÃ³dulo</i><span>&nbsp;</span>o<span>&nbsp;</span><i>magnitud</i><span>&nbsp;</span>de un nÃºmero complejo<span>&nbsp;</span><i>z</i><span>&nbsp;</span>viene dado por la siguiente expresiÃ³n:</p><blockquote style=\"font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; padding: 5px 10px; background-color: white; color: black; text-align: left; margin-left: 30px; margin-bottom: 0.4em; margin-top: 0.2em; min-width: 50%;\"><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit;\"><span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; opacity: 0;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{displaystyle |z|={sqrt {zz^{*}}}={sqrt {{hbox{Re}}^{2}(z)+{hbox{Im}}^{2}(z)}}}</annotation></semantics></math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/461c6dd5195b4c029bf17fcd33137410056f51cb\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline\" aria-hidden=\"true\" alt=\"|z|={sqrt  {zz^{*}}}={sqrt  {{hbox{Re}}^{2}(z)+{hbox{Im}}^{2}(z)}}\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: -1.671ex; margin: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 32.333ex; height: 4.843ex;\"></span></p></blockquote><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Si pensamos en las coordenadas cartesianas del nÃºmero complejo<span>&nbsp;</span><i>z</i>como algÃºn punto en el plano; podemos ver, por el<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teorema_de_Pit%C3%A1goras\" title=\"Teorema de PitÃ¡goras\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;\">teorema de PitÃ¡goras</a>, que el valor absoluto de un nÃºmero complejo coincide con la<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Distancia_eucl%C3%ADdea\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Distancia euclÃ­dea\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;\">distancia euclÃ­dea</a><span>&nbsp;</span>desde el origen del plano a dicho punto.</p><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Si el complejo estÃ¡ escrito en forma exponencial<span>&nbsp;</span><i>z</i><span>&nbsp;</span>=<span>&nbsp;</span><i>r e</i><sup style=\"line-height: 1em;\">iÏ†</sup>, entonces |<i>z</i>| =<span>&nbsp;</span><i>r</i>. Se puede expresar en forma trigonomÃ©trica como<span>&nbsp;</span><i>z</i><span>&nbsp;</span>=<span>&nbsp;</span><i>r</i><span>&nbsp;</span>(cosÏ† + isenÏ†), donde cosÏ† + isenÏ† =<span>&nbsp;</span><i>e</i><sup style=\"line-height: 1em;\">iÏ†</sup><span>&nbsp;</span>es la conocida<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/F%C3%B3rmula_de_Euler\" title=\"FÃ³rmula de Euler\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;\">fÃ³rmula de Euler</a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Podemos comprobar con facilidad estas cuatro importantes propiedades del valor absoluto</p><dl style=\"margin-top: 0.2em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><dd style=\"margin-left: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.1em; margin-right: 0px;\"><span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; opacity: 0;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{displaystyle left|z\r\night|=0Longleftrightarrow z=0}</annotation></semantics></math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/1db0e5714ae2dadf67e43bce0faf1037cd805755\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline\" aria-hidden=\"true\" alt=\"left|z\r\night|=0Longleftrightarrow z=0\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: -0.838ex; display: inline-block; width: 17.599ex; height: 2.843ex;\"></span></dd></dl><dl style=\"margin-top: 0.2em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14p